// Source Code
Terraform [icon: terraform, label: "Terraform (IaC Source Code)"]
GitHub [icon: github, label: "GitHub (Project Repository)"]

// Deployment Flow
Terraform -> TERRAFORM BUILD: Provision infrastructure
GitHub -> Vercel: Pull source code
Vercel -> Next.js App: Deploy frontend UI

// Image Processing Flow
Next.js App -> API Gateway: Upload image
API Gateway -> Lambda: Resize Image
Lambda -> S3 Bucket: Store Resized image
S3 Bucket -> Next.js App: Return image URL
